================================================================================
üíé DESIGN PATTERNS - EXAMPLES
================================================================================

PATTERN 1: FULL-PAGE CENTERED FEATURE
```tsx
import { AppShell } from '@/components/app/AppShell';
import { motion } from 'framer-motion';
import { Play } from 'lucide-react';

export default function CounterPage() {
  const [count, setCount] = React.useState(0);
  
  return (
    <AppShell>
      <div className="flex flex-col items-center justify-center min-h-[70vh] text-center space-y-12">
        {/* Hero Number */}
        <motion.div
          className="text-9xl font-mono font-bold text-gradient glow-primary tabular-nums"
          animate={{ scale: [1, 1.02, 1] }}
          transition={{ duration: 2, repeat: Infinity }}
        >
          {count}
        </motion.div>
        
        {/* Label */}
        <p className="text-xl text-muted-foreground uppercase tracking-widest">
          Total Count
        </p>
        
        {/* Controls */}
        <div className="flex gap-4">
          <button 
            onClick={() => setCount(c => c + 1)}
            className="btn-brand px-12 py-5 text-lg"
          >
            <Play className="w-6 h-6 mr-2" />
            Increment
          </button>
          <button 
            onClick={() => setCount(0)}
            className="btn-brand-outline px-12 py-5 text-lg"
          >
            Reset
          </button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </AppShell>
  );
}
```

PATTERN 2: DASHBOARD WITH CARDS
```tsx
import { AppShell } from '@/components/app/AppShell';
import { Activity, TrendingUp, Users } from 'lucide-react';

export default function DashboardPage() {
  const stats = [
    { label: 'Active Users', value: '1,234', icon: Users, change: '+12%' },
    { label: 'Total Revenue', value: '$45.2K', icon: TrendingUp, change: '+8%' },
    { label: 'Activity', value: '892', icon: Activity, change: '+23%' }
  ];
  
  return (
    <AppShell>
      <div className="space-y-8">
        <h1 className="text-5xl font-bold text-gradient">
          Dashboard
        </h1>
        
        <div className="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
          {stats.map(stat => (
            <div key={stat.label} className="glass-panel p-8 space-y-4 group hover:scale-105 transition-transform">
              <div className="flex items-center justify-between">
                <span className="text-sm text-muted-foreground uppercase tracking-wide">
                  {stat.label}
                </span>
                <stat.icon className="w-8 h-8 text-primary opacity-50 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity" />
              </div>
              
              <div className="text-4xl font-bold font-mono text-gradient">
                {stat.value}
              </div>
              
              <div className="text-sm text-green-400">
                {stat.change}
              </div>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>
    </AppShell>
  );
}
```

PATTERN 3: FORM WITH GLASS PANELS
```tsx
import { AppShell } from '@/components/app/AppShell';
import { Input } from '@/components/ui/input';
import { Textarea } from '@/components/ui/textarea';

export default function FormPage() {
  return (
    <AppShell>
      <div className="max-w-2xl mx-auto space-y-8">
        <h1 className="text-5xl font-bold text-gradient text-center">
          Contact Form
        </h1>
        
        <div className="glass-panel p-10 space-y-6">
          <div className="space-y-2">
            <label className="text-sm font-medium text-muted-foreground uppercase tracking-wide">
              Name
            </label>
            <Input 
              placeholder="Enter your name"
              className="bg-background/50 border-border"
            />
          </div>
          
          <div className="space-y-2">
            <label className="text-sm font-medium text-muted-foreground uppercase tracking-wide">
              Message
            </label>
            <Textarea 
              placeholder="Your message..."
              className="bg-background/50 border-border min-h-[150px]"
            />
          </div>
          
          <button className="btn-brand w-full py-4 text-lg font-medium">
            Send Message
          </button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </AppShell>
  );
}
```

================================================================================
‚ú® ANIMATION BEST PRACTICES
================================================================================

Use framer-motion for smooth interactions:

1. ENTRANCE ANIMATIONS (handled by AppShell, but can add more):
   ```tsx
   <motion.div
     initial={{ opacity: 0, y: 20 }}
     animate={{ opacity: 1, y: 0 }}
     transition={{ duration: 0.6 }}
   >
     {content}
   </motion.div>
   ```

2. PULSE/BREATHING EFFECTS:
   ```tsx
   <motion.div
     animate={{ scale: [1, 1.05, 1], opacity: [0.8, 1, 0.8] }}
     transition={{ duration: 3, repeat: Infinity, ease: "easeInOut" }}
   >
     {content}
   </motion.div>
   ```

3. HOVER INTERACTIONS:
   ```tsx
   <motion.button
     whileHover={{ scale: 1.05 }}
     whileTap={{ scale: 0.95 }}
   >
     {content}
   </motion.button>
   ```

